<div class="back_main">
    <div class="back_main_title">
        <span>发票与报销</span>
    </div>
    <div class="back_main_content">
        <div class="back_main_tips">
            <p>1.平台收取的报价服务费，开票方为湖北省楚建易网络科技有限公司；</p>
            <p>2.累计报价消费金额不小于300元，可在平台申请开票。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="back_main_search">
                <label>订购时间：</label><input type="text" class="cjy-calendar-input" name="start_time" placeholder="订购开始时间" calendar readonly>
            <span class="search_line">-</span>
            <input type="text" class="cjy-calendar-input" name="end_time" placeholder="订购结束时间" calendar readonly>
            <input type="checkbox" name="is_invoice" title="未开票">
            <div class="search_btn_con">
                <a href="javascript:;" class="back_btn_search marginR10">搜索</a>
                <a href="javascript:;" class="back_btn_clear">清空</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="orderList">
            <div class="back_main_nav clearfix">
                <span class="textBlack1 marginR24">共{{count}}条记录</span>
                <span class="textBlack1 marginR24">购买报价总次数<span class="textRed">{{allNum}}</span>次</span>
                <span class="textBlack1 marginR24">消费总金额<span class="textRed">{{allMoney}}</span>元</span>
            </div>
            <div class="back_main_list">
                <div class="material_list">
                    <table>
                        <colgroup>
                            <col width="100">
                            <col width="200">
                            <col width="200">
                            <col width="200">
                            <col width="200">
                        </colgroup>
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th><input type="checkbox" class="js_checkAll" title="全选"></th>
                                <th>订购报价次数</th>
                                <th>消费金额</th>
                                <th>订购时间</th>
                                <th>状态</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody class="product_tbody" id="productList">
                        <tr v-if="list.length>0" v-for="item in list">
                            <td><input type="checkbox" :value="item.id" class="js_checkSingle" title="" v-if="item.is_invoice=='0'"></td>
                            <td>{{item.quote_time}}次</td>
                            <td>￥{{item.total_price}}</td>
                            <td>{{item.create_time}}</td>
                            <td><span class="textRed" v-if="item.is_invoice=='0'">未开票</span><span class="textGreen" v-if="item.is_invoice=='1'">已申请</span><span class="textBlack3" v-if="item.is_invoice=='2'">已开票</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr v-if="list.length<=0">
                            <td colspan="5" v-if="!loading">
                                <div class="page_list_noneBg"></div>
                                <p class="page_list_noneCon" style="width: 100%;margin-bottom: 60px;font-size: 24px;color: #999;text-align: center;">没有找到相关内容</p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr v-if="list.length>0">
                            <td colspan="5">
                                <div class="invoice_footer">
                                    <input type="checkbox" class="js_checkAll" title="全选">
                                    <a href="javascript:;" :class="{'invoiceApplay':btnActive,'invoiceApplayDisabled':!btnActive}" @click="applayCheck()">申请开票</a>
                                    <span class="floatR">已选<span class="textRed js_totalNum">{{totalNum}}</span>条，共<span class="textRed js_totalMoney">{{totalMoney}}</span>元（满300元开票）</span>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                    <div class="clear"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>